---
title: SuperQuick Beef Tacos with Red Cabbage and Sweet Bell Pepper Slaw
description: These speedy beef tacos are a great way to get supper on the table in no time flat. Start the beef and pre-chopped onions on the stove and assemble the rest of the components as they cook.

